PN,41201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FA major independent review into
OL,8,Fmaternity services at four Sussex
OL,9,Fhospitals will examine more than a
OL,10,F1,000 cases from a ten year period.
OL,12,FThe inquiry, led by respected former
OL,13,Fmidwife Donna Ockenden, will not only
OL,14,Flook into the deaths of babies at
OL,15,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS Trust
OL,16,Fbut also instances of harm experienced
OL,17,Fby mothers during the delivery of
OL,18,Ftheir child.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FBereaved families who last month
OL,8,Fconvinced the Health Secretary that a
OL,9,Ffull, independent review was
OL,10,Fnecessary, have welcomed the decision
OL,11,Fthat it will be an opt-out review, to
OL,12,Fhelp deliver 'meaningful change'.
OL,14,FIt means families who've received care
OL,15,Fat the Royal Sussex County in
OL,16,FBrighton, Worthing, Princess Royal in
OL,17,FHaywards Heath and St Richard's in
OL,18,FChichester will automatically be
OL,19,Fincluded unless they choose not to be
OL,20,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FEvidence from patients will be
OL,8,Fgathered from around a 10-year period
OL,9,Fstarting from 2018 up to a year before
OL,10,Fthe Ockenden report is published,
OL,11,Fwhich could take around between two
OL,12,Fand three years from now.
OL,14,FThe Truth for Our Babies Campaign
OL,15,Fsaid, "We are confident that the scope
OL,16,Fof this review, led by Donna Ockenden
OL,17,Fand supported by her large multi-
OL,18,Fprofessional team will ensure that all
OL,19,Fvoices are heard and importantly acted
OL,20,Fupon."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FLiz Charlton, who joined the group
OL,8,Ffollowing the stillbirth of her baby
OL,9,Fdaughter Hazel says the scope which
OL,10,Fhas been agreed is what families have
OL,11,Fbeen fighting for.
OL,13,FShe said, "I feel like all our hard
OL,14,Fwork has really paid off, and it's
OL,15,Fbeen ultimately all for our babies
OL,16,Fhave been driving us, All of us and
OL,17,Four group that have lost our babies is
OL,18,Fwhat has kept us going.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"There's many people that haven't felt
OL,8,Ftheir voices have been heard, and also
OL,9,Feveryone is navigating their own
OL,10,Ftrauma and grief, in their own way.
OL,11,FAnd this means that someone can carry
OL,12,Fthat for them, without them having to
OL,13,Fhave the weight themselves.
OL,15,FBereaved mother Liz Charlton says the
OL,16,Fscope of the inquiry presents a huge
OL,17,Fturning point for families
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"As I've always said, you've got to
OL,8,Fhave every part of that to be, to be
OL,9,Fable to say what is needed, what
OL,10,Ftrends there are, what's reoccurring,
OL,11,Fthose systematic failings to support
OL,12,Ffamilies is the future.
OL,14,F"People want to be able to go and have
OL,15,Fsafe maternity care and this is the
OL,16,Fbest way to do that, so change is
OL,17,Fcoming and is what we need."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe Sussex review will be the fourth
OL,8,Fto be carried out into NHS maternity
OL,9,Ftrusts in England by Donna Ockenden
OL,10,Fsince 2017.
OL,12,FThe healthcare leader with more than
OL,13,F35 years experience is the only person
OL,14,Ffamilies trust and have confidence to
OL,15,Fdeliver change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FHer work on services at Shrewsbury and
OL,8,FTelford found concerns with the care
OL,9,Fof 250 cases, whilst her ongoing
OL,10,Fexamination of Nottingham neonatal
OL,11,Fcare has so far covered around 2,500
OL,12,Fcases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FDonna said, "It's a privilege to have
OL,8,Fthe trust of so many families across
OL,9,FSussex. Family voices will run through
OL,10,Fthe heart of the Review; their
OL,11,Fperspective is essential in ensuring
OL,12,Fthat the Review is fully inclusive and
OL,13,Freflective of their experiences (what
OL,14,Fhas happened to them), and meets their
OL,15,Fneeds.
OL,26,@oD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FTogether with families, we will
OL,8,Fdevelop the Terms of Reference of the
OL,9,FReview to make sure that all families
OL,10,Fhave the opportunity for their voice
OL,11,Fto be heard ` especially
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged, seldom heard and global
OL,13,Fmajority families.
OL,15,F"My team and I are fully committed to
OL,16,Fensuring that hearing from and
OL,17,Flearning from family experiences and
OL,18,Fthe voices of current and former staff
OL,19,F'on the ground' across Sussex will
OL,20,Fshape improvements at the Trust to the
OL,21,Fbenefit of both families and staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"As we progress through the Review my
OL,8,Fteam and I will share learning from
OL,9,Fwhat we hear from families and staff.
OL,10,FThis will help shape improvements so
OL,11,Fthat local communities can feel
OL,12,Fconfident that maternity care is
OL,13,Fimproving whilst our work is ongoing."
OL,15,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex says it
OL,16,Fwelcomes external scrutiny and changes
OL,17,Fhave been in recent years to
OL,18,Fstrengthen care.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FIt points to the perinatal mortality
OL,8,Frate being at 2.3 deaths per a
OL,9,Fthousand births, less than half the
OL,10,Fnational average of 4.7 per a thousand
OL,11,Fbirths, and that 40 additional
OL,12,Fmidwifes have recruited.
OL,14,FBut data received by ITV Meridian
OL,15,Fshows independent body the Maternity
OL,16,Fand Newborn Safety Investigations
OL,17,FTeam, used to investigate baby deaths
OL,18,For severe brain injuries, shows
OL,19,Fmultiple safety recommendations have
OL,20,Falready been made to trust since
OL,21,FOctober 2023.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FIn more than 13 of over 23 cases
OL,8,Finvestigated up to February this year,
OL,9,Fissues were highlighted on in areas
OL,10,Fincluding Fetal Monitoring, Clinical
OL,11,FAssessment and Escalation procedures,
OL,12,Fsometimes more than once.
OL,14,FAlthough the MNSI also investigated
OL,15,Falmost 1,500 cases nationally in that
OL,16,Fsame period, families who've lost
OL,17,Fchildren in Sussex say repeated issues
OL,18,Fneed to be rectified and the Ockenden
OL,19,Freview will achieve that.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FChelsea Gowar and Oliver Thompson lost
OL,8,Ftheir daughter Bonnie after she spent
OL,9,Fweeks in intensive care.
OL,11,FChelsea said, "If all of these things
OL,12,Fare a problem, how are they still
OL,13,Fhappening? Because there are parents
OL,14,Fin this group that lost their children
OL,15,Fin 2021. I lost my daughter in 2025.
OL,16,FThat's four years down the line.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"I don't think anything can ever make
OL,8,Famends. I think once you have
OL,9,Fexperienced what we what we have, I
OL,10,Fdon't think there's anything that will
OL,11,Fever take that pain away.
OL,13,F"I think somebody taking
OL,14,Faccountability and knowing that things
OL,15,Fare going to be different for future
OL,16,Ffamilies, that will be something that
OL,17,Fbrings me comfort.
OL,19,FChelsea says she will take comfort
OL,20,Ffrom knowing the review might bring
OL,21,Fdifferent outcomes for other families
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"As parents it is hard to do the fight
OL,8,Fbecause you're not only grieving your
OL,9,Fchild, you are then having to fight
OL,10,Ffor answers that we should have never
OL,11,Fhad to fight for.
OL,13,F"We should just be given the truth.
OL,14,FThey should just take accountability
OL,15,Fand there should just be an apology.
OL,16,FYou shouldn't have to fight and shout
OL,17,Freally loudly, ultimately to be heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"I think the fact that we are doing
OL,8,Fsuch a long period of time will really
OL,9,Fenable us to say when things changed,
OL,10,Fwhat happened and whether or not
OL,11,Fthings could have been done
OL,12,Fdifferently and what the trust can
OL,13,Fultimately do in the future to prevent
OL,14,Fmore families being in the situation
OL,15,Fthat we're in, because that's
OL,16,Fultimately what's important."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FOlivier said, "The fact that the
OL,8,Finquiry's been pushed ahead and it's
OL,9,Fgoing to be such a vast period of
OL,10,Ftime, I think it's going to enable
OL,11,Flots of families to get that insight
OL,12,Fof what's actually been going on
OL,13,Fbehind the scenes.
OL,15,F"Hopefully now this fight is out of
OL,16,Four hands, we can all, as a group,
OL,17,Ftake a step back and and actually
OL,18,Fgrieve properly for what we've truly
OL,19,Flost.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G18/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FOliver says he's pleased there has
OL,8,Fbeen progress so quickly after the
OL,9,Freview was granted
OL,11,F"We've been dealt the cards that we've
OL,12,Fbeen dealt and there's there's nothing
OL,13,Fthat's going to change that. We've
OL,14,Flost our daughter now and there's
OL,15,Fnothing that's going to bring her back.
OL,17,F"What we want is things to change to
OL,18,Fother families and other people don't
OL,19,Fhave to experience what we've had to
OL,20,Fexperience because it's just been
OL,21,Fawful.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G19/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778746039
OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"And it if it could have been
OL,8,Favoidable, or if it could have been
OL,9,Favoided, then I think people should be
OL,10,Fheld accountable for that."
OL,12,FDr Andy Heeps, Chief Executive
OL,13,FOfficer, University Hospitals Sussex
OL,14,FNHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,16,F"Our thoughts remain first and
OL,17,Fforemost with the families whose
OL,18,Fbabies have died or who have suffered
OL,19,Fharm when receiving care in our
OL,20,Fhospitals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G20/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
