OL,3,CMaternity care of 1,000+ NHS Sussex
OL,4,Ccases to be reviewed following baby
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"The scope we have set out is
OL,8,Fdeliberately broad and inclusive with
OL,9,Fall eligible cases included
OL,10,Fautomatically unless families choose
OL,11,Fotherwise.
OL,13,F"Donna Ockenden has already shown,
OL,14,Ftime and again, that she has the
OL,15,Fexpertise and confidence of the
OL,16,Ffamilies to lead a thorough review,
OL,17,Fand I have every confidence she will
OL,18,Fdo the same in Sussex."
